title: World of Firepower November/December 2014
description:
World of Firepower November/December 2014

eared toward the gun enthusiast, Firepower captures the lifestyle that is firearms. In the course of the journey through these 132 pages, readers may be thrust into an adrenaline-filled SWAT raid or find themselves smack in the middle of Africa on a safari. Plus in addition to reading about the hottest firearms on the market and the latest in bad ass tactical gear readers can chill with the hottest gear and equipment that supports their avocation, such as diesel trucks, tactical knives, binoculars and other outdoor gadgets
